dct_description_sm: Town plan surrounded by 6 views of buildings and bird's-eye view of city. Inset map of area between Junction City and Fort Riley, Kansas. Historic Maps copy has ms. notes in a contemporary hand identifying unnamed views.
dct_publisher_sm: St. Louis, Mo. : Juls. Hutawa, lith., [ca. 1870]
